   319Ôćĺ## Agents
   323Ôćĺ> Software is changing, and dotenv must change with itÔÇöthat is why I built [agentic secret storage (AS2)](https://dotenvx.com/as2). Agents run code without humans at terminals, so plaintext `.env` files are the wrong primitive.
   324Ôćĺ>
